repair.repairedDockerfile:
FROM node:lts-alpine

ARG PORT=80
ENV PORT=$PORT
ENV NODE_ENV production
EXPOSE $PORT

RUN mkdir -p /simulado
WORKDIR /simulado
ADD . /simulado
RUN npm install

CMD ["npm", "start"]
